  "title": "Cleaning Supervisor - Commercial Building",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Supervising multiple team of cleaners for difference projects.</li>\n  <li>Ensure service quality delivery and safety of all our employees. </li>\n  <li>Assist in planning of cleaning service operations work plans.</li>\n  <li>Assist in incident management. </li>\n  <li>Managing inventory of the cleaning equipment and materials used in multiple project sites. </li>\n  <li>Provide guidance and coaching of new team members.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job requisite:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>May be assigned to a variety of places including indoor and outdoor public places. </li>\n  <li>Must be comfortable to communicate with stakeholders.</li>\n  <li>Prior supervisory experience in service industry is an added advantage.</li>\n</ul>",
